{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"mutating"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"optimizeForWeight"},{"kind":"text","text":"()"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":2,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/dndengine\/dndcoins\/optimizeforweight()"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/DnDEngine\/documentation\/DnDEngine\/DnDCoins\/optimizeForWeight()","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Combines coins into their higher value equivalent so that the pouch contains the fewest"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"coin pieces possible and thereby reducing the total weight of the pouch."}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"optimizeForWeight"},{"kind":"text","text":"()"}],"title":"optimizeForWeight()","roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:9DnDEngine0A6DCoinsV17optimizeForWeightyyF","modules":[{"name":"DnDEngine"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/DnDEngine\/documentation\/DnDEngine","doc:\/\/DnDEngine\/documentation\/DnDEngine\/DnDCoins"]]},"references":{"doc://DnDEngine/documentation/DnDEngine/DnDCoins/optimizeForWeight()":{"role":"symbol","title":"optimizeForWeight()","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"optimizeForWeight"},{"kind":"text","text":"()"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Combines coins into their higher value equivalent so that the pouch contains the fewest"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"coin pieces possible and thereby reducing the total weight of the pouch."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/DnDEngine\/documentation\/DnDEngine\/DnDCoins\/optimizeForWeight()","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/dndengine\/dndcoins\/optimizeforweight()"},"doc://DnDEngine/documentation/DnDEngine":{"role":"collection","title":"DnDEngine","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A powerful engine for DnD games and applications"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/DnDEngine\/documentation\/DnDEngine","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/dndengine"},"doc://DnDEngine/documentation/DnDEngine/DnDCoins":{"role":"symbol","title":"DnDCoins","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"DnDCoins"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Common coins come in several different denominations based on the relative"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"worth of the metal from which they are made. The three most common coins"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"are the gold piece (gp), the silver piece (sp), and the copper piece (cp)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"With one gold piece, a character can buy a bedroll, 50 feet of good rope,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or a goat. A skilled (but not exceptional) artisan can earn one gold piece"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a day. The gold piece is the standard unit of measure for wealth, even if"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the coin itself is not commonly used. When merchants discuss deals that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"involve goods or services worth hundreds or thousands of gold pieces, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transactions donâ€™t usually involve the exchange of individual coins."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Rather, the gold piece is a standard measure of value, and the actual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"exchange is in gold bars, letters of credit, or valuable goods."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/DnDEngine\/documentation\/DnDEngine\/DnDCoins","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"DnDCoins"}],"url":"\/documentation\/dndengine\/dndcoins"}}}